title: Boonk on Getting his Jaw Broken, Passing out Last Time on No Jumper, New Record Deal
description:
Last time Boonk was on No Jumper he passed out head first into the wall. This time he returned to explain what was going on that time, why he recently got punched in the face and had to get his jaw wired and what else he's been up to in his life. --- 0:43 Introducing John Gabbana 1:07 Boonk vs John Gabbana 1:58 Passed out last time you were here 3:18 Most viral moment 3:52 Did your entourage care 5:20 Clout 5:58 Kid Buu 6:13 What happened in your life after that incident 7:40 New IG account 9:00 Being locked up 11:50 Probation 13:30 Jaw broken with permanent grills 14:44 New record deal 16:02 Not ready for fame, music was trash + regretting what he did for clout 17:58 Doing anything for clout 18:34 People copy Boonk 19:07 People think I'm funny, I'm not a comedian 19:40 Using this fame the right way + playing solitary 20:41 Wrote a book 22:22 New found behavior, new girlfriend 23:48 Depression and seeing a therapist 27:38 Face tatts 28:40 Peer pressure 30:00 Remix with Nicki Minaj 31:31 John Gabbana is wiser 34:53 The meme formula 36:56 Bible study 37:54 How was the life in jail? 38:54 Asking PO permission to still do gigs 41:15 Being away from social media and rebuilding his brand --- FOLLOW OUR NEW SPOTIFY PLAYLIST! https://spoti.fi/2vi9lsD CHECK OUT OUR ONLINE STORE!!! http://www.nojumper.com/ SUBSCRIBE for new interviews (and more) weekly: http://bit.ly/nastymondayz Follow us on Soundcloud: https://soundcloud.com/nojumper and iTunes: https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/no-jumper/id1001659715?mt=2 and follow us on Social Media: http://www.twitter.com/nojumper http://www.instagram.com/nojumper http://www.reddit.com/r/nojumper JOIN THE DISCORD: https://discord.gg/Q3XPfBm follow Adam22 as well: http://www.twitter.com/adam22 http://www.instagram.com/adam22 and follow adam22hoe on Snapchat
